      <div class="container">
         <div class="document">

            <h2 class="point">How to use Quick-Add-Event</h2>

            <p>You can enter natural sentence like “10:00-12:00 Meeting at Shibuya” when create new event.
            Enter a title, date, and time duration for the event, and then press Return.</p>
            <p><img class="quick img-rounded" src="./quick-en.png" /></p>

            <hr />

            <div class="row">
               <div class="span4" align="center">
                  <div class="subheader text-left">
                     <h2 id="use" class="checkbox">Formats</h2>
                  </div>
               </div>

               <div class="span8">

                  <h3 class="point">Basic rule</h3>
                  <ul>
                     <li>If you enter any date or days of the week, Calendar set a next date (week).</li>
                     <li>If you don't enter any time information, Calendar makes the event an all-day event.</li>
                     <li>If you don't enter a time duration, Calendar sets the duration to 1 hour.</li>
                  </ul>

                  <h3 class="point">Common formats</h3>
                  <ul>
                     <li>7pm Meeting</li>
                     <li>10-12 Meeting</li>
                     <li>10:00-12:00 Meeting at Shibuya</li>
                     <li>6/11 19-22 Meeting</li>
                     <li>Meeting Friday from 11am-1pm</li>
                  </ul>


                  <h3 class="point">Specified time</h3>
                  <ul>
                     <li>10am - 1pm Meeting</li>
                     <li>4:00 pm - 9:30 Meeting</li>
                     <li>2:15 - 3 p.m. Meeting</li>
                     <li>14:15 Meeting</li>
                  </ul>


                  <h3 class="point">Specified a day of week</h3>
                  <ul>
                     <li>Meeting on Friday</li>
                     <li>Meeting next Friday</li>
                     <li>Meeting Friday at 7pm</li>
                  </ul>


                  <h3 class="point">Specified date</h3>
                  <ul>
                     <li>Meeting 6/11</li>
                     <li>6.11 15:30 Meeting</li>
                     <li>5.1 Meeting</li>
                     <li>10:00-12:00 Meeting tomorrow</li>
                  </ul>


               </div>
            </div>

            <hr />

